import { AppBar, IconButton, Toolbar, Typography } from "@mui/material"
import Box from '@mui/material/Box';
import { MenuOutlinedIcon, DarkModeIcon, AccountCircle } from '../icons'

export const NavBar = () => {
    return (
        <Box sx={{ flexGrow: 1 }}>
            <AppBar position='sticky'>
                <Toolbar>
                    <IconButton size='large' edge='start'>
                        <MenuOutlinedIcon />
                    </IconButton>
                    <Typography variant='h6'>myOwnChefBook</Typography>
                    <IconButton size='large' edge='end'>
                        <DarkModeIcon />
                    </IconButton>
                    <IconButton
                        size="large"
                        aria-label="account of current user"
                        aria-controls="menu-appbar"
                        aria-haspopup="true"
                        // onClick={handleMenu}
                        color="inherit"
                    >
                        <AccountCircle />
                    </IconButton>
                </Toolbar>
            </AppBar>
        </Box>
    )
}
